when%20agents%20are%20overloaded%20with%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%20in%20their%20%26quot%3Bcontext%20window%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20part%20of%20the%20process%20where%20models%20synthesize%20information%20before%20generating%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20trusting%20one%20super-agent%20to%20handle%20everything%2C%20Levie%20said%20the%20smarter%20approach%20is%20to%20carve%20up%20the%20work%20and%20assign%20it%20to%20fleets%20of%20specialized%20sub-agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20break%20apart%20the%20agents%20and%20the%20context%20that%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20have%20multiple%20agents%2C%20all%20with%20a%20set%20of%20goals%20and%20a%20set%20of%20contexts%20that%20are%20germane%20to%20their%20particular%20part%20of%20the%20workflow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20counter-trend%20to%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20dream%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-super-agents-enough-computing-power-openai-deepseek-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle%20AGI%20overlord%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Levie%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-native-grads-will-outperform-junior-engineers-says-box-ceo-levie-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecofounded%20Box%20in%202005%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20sub-agent%20model%20is%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20going%20to%20be%20the%20future%20of%20large-scale%20agent%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20also%20said%20the%20key%20to%20better%20AI%20performance%20is%20to%20give%20these%20models%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20accurate%20information%20and%20just%20the%20most%20precise%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20both%20very%20precise%20in%20your%20instructions%20and%20then%20you%20have%20to%20give%20the%20model%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20the%20right%20context%20to%20operate%20from%2C%20but%20too%20muc