0the%20former%20chief%20information%20officer%20for%20the%20US%20General%20Services%20Administration%2C%20says%20AI%20will%20allow%20federal%20workers%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Bbetter%2C%20more%20creative%2C%20higher-value%20work.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EServiceNow%3B%20J.%20David%20Ake%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECasey%20Coleman%2C%2060%2C%20was%20the%20chief%20information%20officer%20for%20the%20GSA%20from%202007%20to%202014.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20AI%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20federal%20workers%20to%20get%20things%20done.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20and%20Google%20are%20offering%20federal%20agencies%20access%20to%20their%20AI%20models%20at%20essentially%20no%20cost.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20Coleman%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20information%20officer%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-admin-gsa-doge-consultants-contracts-justify-spend-deloitte-accenture-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20General%20Services%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20giving%20federal%20workers%20access%20to%20AI%20will%20result%20in%20more%20higher-value%20work%20being%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColeman%2C%2060%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20this%20month%20that%20when%20she%20was%20in%20government%2C%20she%20often%20struggled%20to%20identify%20the%20right%20agencies%20she%20had%20to%20work%20with%20to%20get%20things%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20done%20in%20concert%20with%20multiple%20stakeholders%2C%20and%20so%20workflows%20involve%20approvals%20from%20different%20groups%2C%20and%20sometimes%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20who%20could%20approve%20a%20particular%20course%20of%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20automating%20those%20processes%2C%20being%20able%20to%20connect%20the%20dots%20across%20organizations%2C%20will%20help%20give%20people%20their%20time%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20a%20net%20benefit%20to%20all%20of%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColeman%20worked%20at%20the%20GSA%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20was%20its%20chief%20information%20officer%20from%202007%20to%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20leaving%20government%2C%20she's%20worked%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20Unisys%2C%20and%20Salesforce.%20She%20joined%20ServiceNow%2C%20a%20California-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-top-engineers-servicenow-pat-casey-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecloud%20and%20AI%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202025%2C%20and%20oversees%20its%20public%20sector%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20go%20into%20public%20service%20to%20serve%20and%20to%20give%20back.%20They%20don't%20go%20to%20manage%20bureaucratic%20workflows%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColeman%20said%20rolling%20out%20AI%20is%20unlikely%20to%20result%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-job-cuts-how-when-firings-could-happen-for-workers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efewer%20government%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20she%20said%20that%20AI%20would%20raise%20productivity%20and%20quality%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20own%20experience%2C%20we%20always%20had%20so%20much%20more%20work%20to%20do%20than%20we%20could%20possibly%20get%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20think%20about%20the%20things%20we%20can%20do%20now%20that%20we%20couldn't%20do%20in%20the%20past%20because%20we%20have%20better%20technology.%20It's%20not%20that%20we%20are%20going%20to%20need%20fewer%20people.%20It's%20that%20we%20are%20doing%20better%2C%20more%20creative%2C%20higher-value%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20said%20they%20were%20offering%20federal%20agencies%20a%20year's%20access%20to%20their%20AI%20models%20at%20a%20nominal%20cost%20of%20%241.%20Op