company%2C%20has%20cut%20staff%20and%20closed%20down%20its%20long-running%20devices%20program%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20were%20announced%20internally%20on%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20sent%20to%20staff%20by%20CEO%20Stephen%20Gillett%20and%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerily%2C%20which%20began%20life%20as%20a%20moonshot%20inside%20Google's%20X%20lab%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20cut%20costs%20and%20streamline%20projects.%20The%20group%20has%20refocused%20its%20strategy%20around%20AI%20and%20developing%20infrastructure%20for%20other%20companies%20to%20lean%20on%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fverily-fundraise-2025-ai-strategy-google-breakup-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGillett%20told%20staff%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20part%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20changes%20were%20due%20to%20a%20decision%20to%20wind%20down%20Verily's%20devices%20program%2C%20which%20was%20responsible%20for%20an%20array%20of%20projects%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fverily.com%2Fperspectives%2Fstudy-watch-another-step-closer-to-powering-precision-health%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20clinical%20study%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20retinal%20camera%2C%20and%20a%20partnership%20with%20Dexcom%20for%20its%20wearable%20glucose%20sensor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20years%2C%20Verily%20has%20built%20a%20legacy%20in%20developing%20world-class%2C%20innovative%20medical%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20Gillett%20wrote%20in%20the%20email.%20%26quot%3BThe%20dedicated%20professionals%20in%20our%20Devices%20organizations%20%E2%80%94%20many%20who%20have%20devoted%20a%20decade%20or%20more%20to%20this%20important%20work%20%E2%80%94%20have%20poured%20their%20hearts%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20commitment%20into%20advancing%20healthcare%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20number%20of%20employees%20cut%20could%20not%20be%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20normal%20business%20operations%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20make%20deliberate%20choices%20about%20resourcing%20where%20we%20can%20have%20the%20greatest%20impact%20and%20to%20put%20ourselves%20on%20a%20faster%20path%20to%20sustained%20commercial%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Verily%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20They%20added%20that%20Verily%20has%20been%20on%20a%20strategic%20refocus%20since%202023%20that%20has%20involved%20streamlining%20and%20simplifying%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20the%20difficult%20decision%20to%20discontinue%20manufacturing%20medical%20devices%20and%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20supporting%20them%20going%20forward.%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20still%20owned%20by%20Google's%20holding%20company%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20Verily%20has%20been%20gradually%20detaching%20from%20the%20technology%20and%20services%20it%20long%20shared%20with%20Google.%20Company%20leaders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fverily-leave-google-alphabet-flywheel-life-sciences-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20told%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20efforts%20are%20important%20to%20one%20day%20becoming%20a%20fully%20independent%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20sold%20its%20insurance%20business%20to%20Elevance%20Health%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fverily-enters-agreement-to-sell-its-insurance-business-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20staff%20benefits%20have%20been%20cut%20in%20recent%20months%20while%20employee%20salary%20bands%20have%20been%20re-benchmarked%20to%20the%20healthcare%2C%20rather%20than%20technology%2C%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20two%20employees%20familiar%20with%20the%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20full%20memo%20sent%20by%20Gillett%20to%20Verily%20employees%20on%20Monday%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EVeeps%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI'm%20writing%20to%20share%20some%20difficult%20news.%20Today%20we%20have%20made%20workforce%20reductions%20across%20the%20company%20as%20part%20of%20our%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20manage%20costs%20and%20ensure%20resources%20are%20allocated%20to%20our%20most%20critical%20priorities.%20All%20impacted%20Veeps%20have%20been%20notified.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThese%20are%20not%20decisions%20we've%20taken%20lightly%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20address%20both%20those%20who%20will%20be%20impacted%20and%20those%20who%20will%20continue%20with%20us%20on%20Verily's%20journey.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EA%20significant%20part%20of%20these%20changes%20is%20the%20decision%20to%20wind%20down%20our%20Devices%20program.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Verily%20has%20built%20a%20legacy%20in%20developing%20world-class%2C%20innovative%20medical%20devices.%20The%20dedicated%20professionals%20in%20our%20Devices%20organizations%20%E2%80%94%20many%20who%20have%20devoted%20a%20decade%20or%20more%20to%20this%20important%20work%20%E2%80%94%20have%20poured%20their%20hearts%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20commitment%20into%20advancing%20healthcare%20technology.%20To%20everyone%20who%20contributed%20to%20this%20program%2C%20whether%20as%20a%20core%20team%20member%20or%20in%20a%20supporting%20role%20across%20the%20company%2C%20your%20efforts%20have%20been%20extraordinary.%20You've%20led%20groundbreaking%20achievements%2C%20from%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Dexcom%20G7%20CGM%2C%20to%20the%20Stargazer%20VNRC%20launch%20with%20other%207%2C800%20patients%20screened%2C%20to%20Study%20Devices%20launched%20with%20numerous%20study%20partners%2C%20and%20these%20contributions%20have%20advanced%20patient%20care%20and%20medical%20research.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAs%20Verily%20has%20continued%20on%20its%20journey%20of%20narrowing%20product%20focus%20around%20o