u've%20been%20deemed%20%26quot%3Boverweight%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bobese%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20doctor%2C%20you%20might%20be%20eligible%2C%20too.%20Regardless%20of%20your%20condition%2C%20your%20new%20mattress%20must%20actively%20improve%20or%20treat%20your%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9de7d67-a9d9-41b5-aae7-70b605e78765%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Why%20use%20HSA%2FFSA%20funds%3F%5C%22%3EWhy%20use%20HSA%2FFSA%20funds%20to%20buy%20a%20mattress%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20answer%20is%3A%20it'll%20save%20you%20money.%20Since%20money%20in%20your%20HSA%20or%20FSA%20is%20pre-taxed%2C%20you%20have%20more%20spending%20power%20using%20these%20funds.%20Your%20HSA%2FFSA%20can%20cover%20sales%20tax%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20FSA%20funds%20are%20%26quot%3Buse%20it%20or%20lose%20it%26quot%3B%20and%20expire%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20If%20you%20have%20leftover%20funds%2C%20using%20them%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20mattress%20prevents%20it%20from%20going%20to%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248e88ae3-7751-4a6b-b2dc-6ec9c161085e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20HSA%2FFSA%20funds%20to%20buy%20a%20mattress%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20use%20HSA%2FFSA%20funds%20to%20buy%20a%20mattress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20your%20HSA%2FFSA%20funds%20to%20buy%20a%20mattress%20is%20simple.%20At%20each%20retailer's%20website%2C%20you'll%20add%20products%20to%20your%20cart%20as%20usual%2C%20and%20when%20you%20get%20to%20the%20payment%20screen%2C%20select%20the%20option%20that%20says%20%26quot%3Bpay%20with%20HSA%2FFSA.%26quot%3B%20This%20will%20lead%20you%20to%20a%20health%20survey.%20Once%20complete%2C%20you'll%20be%20prompted%20to%20check%20out.%20Most%20companies%20recommend%20checking%20out%20with%20your%20personal%20credit%20card%20and%20submitting%20a%20reimbursement%20request%2C%20but%20there's%20also%20the%20option%20to%20pay%20directly%20from%20your%20HSA%2FFSA%20card%2C%20too.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20use%20part%20of%20your%20savings%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20mattress%20but%20don't%20have%20enough%20to%20cover%20the%20entire%20purchase%20in%20your%20account%2C%20then%20put%20it%20on%20your%20normal%20credit%20or%20debit%20card.%20This%20way%2C%20you'll%20easily%20be%20reimbursed%20for%20the%20funds%20you%20do%20use%20without%20making%20the%20cost%20splitting%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20qualify%2C%20you'll%20receive%20an%20electronic%20LMN%20in%20your%20inbox%20within%20about%2024-48%20hours.%20You%20can%20then%20send%20it%20to%20your%20savings%20account%20provider%20to%20start%20your%20reimbursement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20your%20funds%20won't%20fully%20cover%20a%20mattress%20since%20HSA%2FFSA%20funds%20can%20only%20be%20used%20to%20pay%20for%20mattress%20features%20that%20actively%20improve%20your%20health%2C%20like%20cooling%20properties%20or%20extra%20support.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20we%20completed%20the%20survey%20and%20ran%20a%20queen-size%20Purple%20and%20DreamCloud%20mattress%20through%20TrueMed%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20mattress%20was%20covered%2C%20minus%20%24223%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20an%20average%20price%20for%20a%20basic%20mattress.%20It%20even%20covered%20the%20in-home%20setup%20on%20the%20Purple.%20Essentially%2C%20your%20funds%20can%20pay%20up%20to%2090%25%20of%20the%20mattress's%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b55f974c-0b37-4750-a60e-8dd77b4c82c2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Eligible%20mattresses%5C%22%3EWhat%20mattresses%20are%20HSA%2FFSA%20eligible%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20can't%20use%20HSA%20and%20FSA%20funds%20to%20buy%20any%20mattress%20on%20the%20market%2C%20there's%20a%20sizable%20list%20of%20comfortable%20mattresses%20that%20are%20eligible.%20Notably%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110327226wg-20%26h%3Ddd7ca72fb70d1dd7812ec642141bb30f9c2a0f184107a304954b46ca7e222d75%26postID%