ker%20models%20resting%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20stairs%20in%20a%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68aca5bbcfc04e97619bf86b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20compared%20dozens%20of%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20to%20determine%20the%20best.%3Cp%3EScott%20Tharler%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20Bluetooth%20speakers%2C%20I%20tested%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20popular%20options.%20After%20conducting%20in-depth%20research%2C%20I%20arrived%20at%20an%20initial%20group%20of%20prospective%20models.%20Specifically%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20that%20were%20versatile%20enough%20to%20work%20well%20around%20the%20home%20and%20outside.%20I%20then%20got%20hands-on%20with%20dozens%20of%20potential%20picks%20to%20compare%20their%20performance%20and%20determine%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20assessing%20each%20speaker%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20several%20key%20factors%2C%20including%20general%20sound%20quality%2C%20connectivity%20options%2C%20smart%20features%2C%20and%20overall%20value.%20My%20methodology%20is%20informed%20by%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20reviewing%20personal%20audio%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20evaluated%20ease-of-use%20factors%20such%20as%20on-device%20controls%2C%20app%20functionality%2C%20portability%2C%20and%20aesthetics.%20The%20best%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20exude%20well-executed%20design%20and%20purpose%2C%20whether%20they%20blend%20into%20or%20add%20style%20to%20whatever%20space%20they%20occupy.%20In%20that%20way%2C%20they%20can%20be%20thought%20of%20as%20accent%20pieces%20not%20just%20sonically%2C%20but%20visually%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20listened%20to%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20audio%20content%20on%20each%20speaker%2C%20from%20different%20music%20genres%20to%20podcasts%20and%20audiobooks.%20To%20analyze%20performance%2C%20I%20evaluated%20the%20range%20and%20clarity%20of%20the%20bass%2C%20midrange%2C%20and%20treble%20frequencies.%20For%20source%20material%2C%20I%20tapped%20into%20streaming%20services%20such%20as%20Amazon%20Music%2C%20Qobuz%2C%20Spotify%2C%20and%20iHeartRadio.%20To%20better%20isolate%20speakers'%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%2C%20I%20performed%20several%20combinations%20of%20side-by-side%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20thorough%2C%20I%20lived%20with%20these%20wireless%20speakers%20for%20weeks%2C%20playing%20all%20sorts%20of%20audio%20on%20them.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20leaned%20heavily%20on%20their%20Bluetooth%20connections%2C%20but%20I%20also%20tested%20WiFi%20and%20multi-room%20capabilities%20when%20applicable.%20I%20listened%20in%20different-sized%20rooms%20at%20varying%20volumes%20and%20distances%2C%20appropriately%20reflecting%20the%20intended%20use%20cases%20for%20each%20speaker%20based%20on%20their%20size%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214e0dcb1-402d-4ffb-9198-dc84d6b12b7f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20Bluetooth%20speaker%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20Bluetooth%20speaker%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20of%20a%20JBL%20Authentics%20300%20Bluetooth%20speaker.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68aca5eaa17a8c5b40536d67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIntuitive%20physical%20controls%20and%20multiple%20connectivity%20options%20make%20JBL's%20Authentics%20300%20a%20versatile%2C%20easy-to-use%20speaker.%3Cp%3EScott%20Tharler%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntended%20use%20case%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20shopping%20for%20a%20Bluetooth%20speaker%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20determine%20what%20room(s)%20and%20outdoor%20environments%20you're%20likely%20to%20use%20it%20in.%20This%20will%20help%20frame%20the%20speaker's%20power%20and%20directionality%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20If%20a%20speaker%20is%20relatively%20bulky%20and%20heavy%2C%20that%20may%20prevent%20you%20from%20frequently%20moving%20it%20around.%20It%20also%20helps%20when%20the%20speaker%20has%20a%20handy%20grip%20built%20into%20its%20body%20(as%20with%20the%20Sonos%20Move%202%20and%20Lodge%20Solar%20Speaker%204)%20or%20a%20prominent%20handle%20(as%20with%20the%20JBL%20Authentics%20300%2C%20Devialet%20Mania%2C%20and%20Bose%20Portable%20Smart%20Speaker).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20This%20is%20crucial%20for%20any%20Bluetooth%20speaker%20you%20plan%20to%20take%20out%20and%20about%2C%20away%20from%20a%20power%20outlet.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20eight%20to%2012%20hours%20of%20listening%20from%20your%20speaker%20before%20having%20to%20recharge%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnectivity%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20maximize%20the%20stability%20and%20range%20of%20the%20wireless%20connection%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20have%20a%20speaker%20running%20at%20least%20Bluetooth%205.2%20(when%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bluetooth.com%2Fauracast%2Ffaq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAuracast%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20introduced).%20This%20version%20enables%20connecting%20two%20or%20more%20source%20devices%20to%20the%20same%20speaker%2C%20grouping%20multiple%20speakers%20to%20the%20same%20source%20device%2C%20and%20receiving%20public%20audio%20broadcasts.%20Some%20of%20the%20best%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20also%20include%20optional%20WiFi%20connectivity%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20stream%20higher-quality%20music%20from%20anywhere%20your%20wireless%20home%20network%20reaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESound%20quality%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-%20When%20auditioning%20a%20speaker's%20audio%20performance%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20listen%20to%20music%20that%20you're%20very%20familiar%20with%20at%20low%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20high%20volumes%20from%20a%20proper%20distance.%20That%20way%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20properly%20assess%20the%20speaker's%20detail%2C%20distortion%20levels%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20satisfies%20your%20tastes.%20Conversely%2C%20if%20you%20blast%20songs%20that%20you%20don't%20know%20while%20sitting%20right%20next%20to%20a%20large%20speaker%20in%20a%20tiny%20room%2C%20you'll%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20that%20same%20speaker%20will%20realistically%20perform%20in%20your%20actual%20setting%20and%20use%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Don't%20confuse%20this%20with%20price%2C%20which%20you%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20lead%20with.%20Rather%20than%20letting%20an%20arbitrary%20price%20tag%20define%20what%20you%20get%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20first%20consider%20what%20features%20and%20performance%20will%20make%20you%20happy%20and%20then%20look%20for%20a%20matching%20speaker%20solution%20within%20a%20%26quot%3Breasonable%26quot%3B%20price%20range%20(whatever%20that%20means%20to%20you).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Apart%20from%20knowing%20how%20weather-%20and%20water-proof%20a%20speaker%20is%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consider%20how%20and%20where%20you'll%20be%20using%20the%20speaker.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20it'll%20usually%20sit%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20it%20may%20get%20stuff%20spilled%20on%20it.%20If%20it'll%20perch%20somewhere%20in%20the%20living%20room%2C%20probably%20not%20as%20much.%20And%20if%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20taken%20camping%2C%20thrown%20into%20carry-ons%2C%20or%20plopped%20down%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20speaker%20that's%20either%20tough%20enough%20to%20withstand%20all%20that%20commotion%20or%20be%20easily%20replaceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase-of-use%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20can't%20be%20overstated%20since%20it%20plays%20such%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20your%20overall%20enjoyment%20of%20the%20speaker%2C%20from%20its%20initial%20setup%20to%20daily%20use.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20big%20reasons%20we%20adore%20the%20JBL%20Authentics%20300.%20Its%20physical%20buttons%20and%20knobs%20are%20laid%20out%20and%20operated%20in%20an%20intuitive%20way.%20The%20app%20not%20only%20adds%20fun%20features%20and%20fine-grained%20adjustments%20but%20is%20also%20simple%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStyle%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20From%20the%20JBL%20Authentics'%20eye-catching%20%26quot%3Bwaffle%26quot%3B%20grille%20to%20the%20Cleer%20Scene's%20red%20colorway%20to%20the%20Devialet%20Mania's%20giant%20eyeball%20vibe%2C%20how%20unique%20a%20speaker%20looks%20has%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20your%20experience%20of%20it.%20In%20fact%2C%20some%20might%20argue%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20speakers%2C%20aesthetics%20are%20just%20as%20important%20as%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213728356-054f-4cea-828e-c1918ab4d3ad%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Bluetooth%20speaker%20FAQs%5C%22%3EBluetooth%20speaker%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sonos%20Move%202%2C%20Bose%20Portable%20Smart%20Speaker%2C%20and%20Lodge%20Solar%20Speaker%204%20on%20a%20coffee%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68aca656a17a8c5b40536d6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(From%20left%20to%20right)%20Sonos's%20wirelessly%20networked%20Move%202%2C%20Bose's%20Portable%20Smart%20Speaker%2C%20and%20Lodge's%20outdoor%20Solar%20Speaker%204.%3Cp%3EScott%20Tharler%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20Bluetooth%20speaker%20brands%20are%20the%20best%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20speaker%20brand's%20products%20are%20the%20best%20at%20everything%2C%20as%20each%20has%20its%20own%20pros%20and%20cons.%20However%2C%20certain%20brands%20are%20known%20for%20specific%20strengths.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20though%20Bose%20is%20probably%20best%20known%20for%20its%20uber%20comfortable%20and%20effective%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%2C%20it%20also%20produces%20high-quality%20soundbars%20and%20portable%20speakers.%20Its%20Portable%20Smart%20Speaker%20and%20current%20range%20of%20SoundLink%20models%20(Micro%2C%20Plus%2C%20Flex%2C%20and%20Max)%20are%20well-reputed%20for%20offering%20excellent%20build%20quality%20and%20top-notch%20sound%20clarity%20for%20their%20respective%20sizes%2C%20though%20at%20a%20fairly%20premium%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20more%20affordable%20side%2C%20JBL%20has%20a%20stellar%20reputation%20for%20consistently%20producing%20great%20portable%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20of%20all%20sizes%2C%20including%20those%20in%20its%20retro-inspired%20Authentics%20line.%20The%20brand's%20smaller%20Go%20and%20Clip%20models%20are%20decent%20budget%20choices.%20Its%20medium-range%20Flip%2C%20Charge%2C%20and%20Xtreme%20models%20are%20deservedly%20quite%20popular.%20And%20its%20venerable%20PartyBox%20line%20is%20a%20yardstick%20for%20large%20wireless%20party%20speakers.%20Each%20offers%20JBL's%20signature%20clean%2C%20V-shaped%20sound%20(with%20elevated%20bass%20and%20treble)%2C%20flexible%20controls%20in%20the%20app%2C%20solid%20durability%2C%20and%20decent%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESonos's%20soundbars%20are%20perennial%20favorites.%20And%20the%20brand%20recently%20forayed%20into%20the%20world%20of%20headphones%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonos%20Ace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20Sonos%20is%20mostly%20known%20for%20how%20well%20its%20app%20empowers%20wirelessly%20networked%20speakers%20to%20churn%20out%20terrific%20sound%20from%20multiple%20audio%20sources%20around%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20companies%20represent%20some%20of%20the%20best%20Bluetooth%20speaker%20brands%20available%2C%20but%20they're%20far%20from%20the%20only%20quality%20options.%20We%20also%20recommend%20models%20from%20Devialet%2C%20Cleer%20Audio%2C%20and%20Lodge.%20And%20though%20none%20of%20their%20models%20made%20the%20cut%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20brands%20like%20Ultimate%20Ears%2C%20Beats%2C%20Anker%2C%20LG%2C%20Sony%2C%20and%20Marshall%20all%20make%20worthwhile%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20for%20different%20needs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20Bluetooth%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBluetooth%20is%20a%20technology%20that%20can%20transmit%20audio%20wirelessly%20from%20one%20compatible%20device%20to%20another.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20Bluetooth%20speaker%20and%20a%20Bluetooth-compatible%20source%20device%2C%20like%20a%20phone%20or%20computer%2C%20you%20can%20play%20music%20from%20your%20source%20to%20your%20speaker%20without%20any%20cables.%20The%20wireless%20range%20can%20vary%2C%20but%20typical%20Bluetooth%20products%20can%20transmit%20audio%20at%20up%20to%2033%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBluetooth%20compresses%20audio%20when%20it's%20transmitted%2C%20which%20means%20there%20is%20some%20loss%20in%20quality%20compared%20to%20a%20wired%20connection.%20That%20said%2C%20modern%20Bluetooth%20technology%20using%20the%20latest%20audio%20codecs%20can%20minimize%20this%20degradation.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20casual%20listeners%20would%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20hear%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20high-quality%20Bluetooth%20signal%20and%20wired%20audio%20playback.%20However%2C%20audiophiles%20who%20want%20the%20absolute%20best%20sound%20quality%20are%20better%20off%20sticking%20to%20a%20wired%20connection%20or%20opting%20for%20WiFi%20playback%20from%20a%20lossless%20audio%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20waterproof%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20best%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20use%20water-resistant%20designs%2C%20but%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20their%20water%20resistance%20varies.%20If%20a%20speaker's%20specifications%20include%20a%20waterproof%20rating%20where%20the%20last%20number%20is%20a%205%20or%206%20(such%20as%20IP66%2C%20for%20the%20Lodge%20Solar%20Speaker%204)%2C%20that%20means%20it's%20fine%20to%20withstand%20splashes%20and%20rain.%20And%20if%20the%20last%20number%20is%20a%207%20or%208%20(like%20IPX7%2C%20for%20the%20Cleer%20Scene)%2C%20that%20means%20it's%20water%20resistance%20is%20more%20heavy%20duty%20and%20won't%20get%20damaged%20even%20if%20fully%20submerged%20(for%20a%20certain%20period%20of%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-bluetooth-speakers%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756238381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68acaa13cfc04e97619bf8f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-bluetooth-speakers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20Bluetooth%20speakers%20include%20top%20models%20from%20Bose%2C%20Sonos%2C%20JBL%2C%20and%20more.%20Our%20picks%20all%20feature%20built-in%20batteries%20and%20excellent%20sound%20quality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Scott%20Tharler)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-bluetooth-speakers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20hospital%20rejects%20Israel's%20claim%20troops%20'saw%20Hamas%20camera'%20before%20deadly%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756238280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-nasser-hospital-gaza_7001901.jpg%3F20250826173207%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgaza-hospital-rejects-israels-claim-troops-saw-hamas-camera-before-deadly-attack-13418939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20that%20was%20hit%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%2C%20killing%2020%20people%20including%20five%20journalists%2C%20has%20rejected%20the%20Israeli%20military's%20claim%20it%20struck%20the%20facility%20becaus