further%20worsened%20the%20situation.%20With%20more%20concrete%20surfaces%20and%20fewer%20permeable%20zones%2C%20the%20cityscape%20now%20prevents%20natural%20rainwater%20absorption%2C%20leading%20to%20surface%20runoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunicipal%20Commissioner%20Gaurav%20Singh%20Sogarwal%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20drainage%20was%20built%20for%20a%20smaller%20and%20less%20developed%20city.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20monsoons%20dump%20volumes%20it%20was%20never%20meant%20to%20handle.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ageing%20drains%20often%20fail%2C%20especially%20when%20blocked%20by%20waste%20or%20silt%2C%20causing%20backflow%20into%20residential%20areas%20and%20prolonged%20water%20stagnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20severe%20%E2%80%94%20stagnant%20floodwaters%20disrupt%20daily%20life%20for%20days%2C%20damage%20homes%2C%20and%20create%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%20such%20as%20dengue%20and%20cholera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20turning%20point%3A%20Launching%20the%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20the%20Gorakhpur%20Municipal%20Corporation%20partnered%20with%20Canarys%20Automations%20to%20tackle%20this%20systemic%20challenge%20head-on.%20Together%2C%20they%20designed%20and%20implemented%20the%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20brings%20processes%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20people%20together%20to%20manage%20urban%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%20guides%20pump%20operations%2C%20monitors%20water%20levels%20constantly%2C%20and%20deploys%20teams%20precisely%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485263%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%20guides%20pump%20operations%2C%20monitors%20water%20levels%20constantly%2C%20and%20deploys%20teams%20precisely%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%20(UFMC)%2C%20established%20by%20Canarys%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20dedicated%20operational%20hub.%20It%20combines%20real-time%20data%20analysis%2C%20predictive%20forecasting%2C%20and%20close%20coordination%20with%20municipal%20teams%20to%20ensure%20swift%2C%20informed%20responses%20to%20flooding%20and%20improved%20city%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheshadri%20Srinivas%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20from%20Canarys%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20send%20our%20field%20engineers%20directly%20to%20waterlogged%20areas%20and%20known%20hotspots%20during%20rain%20events.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20our%20team%20re